{"tid":920891,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無人運輸前哨！Volvo 自駕卡車進駐挪威採石場　穿越漆黑隧道載送石材","createTime":"2018-11-29T07:18:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-29T09:44:51.000Z","uid":212399,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"93e682e9b376a8ca5529b4e62e89f185ae0c21b3","tid":920891,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T07:18:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.limitlessiq.com/media/post/image/1/3/1330-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.limitlessiq.com%2Fmedia%2Fpost%2Fimage%2F1%2F3%2F1330-2.jpg&h=beb0ac19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然無人車離載客還有段距離，不過載貨已經在商業化的路上。<br />\n挪威的一處採石場，近期導入了 6 輛 Volvo 卡車協助運送石材至港口，不過，這 6 輛卡車並沒有司機，而是憑借自動駕駛技術穿梭隧道、跨越 5 公里路途。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/m4wLPfOz-c4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fm4wLPfOz-c4&d=25Bn80kblrlf5eFaRga00ozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=660427dd\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/m4wLPfOz-c4</a><br />\nVolvo 自駕卡車將提供「無人運輸」服務，協助採石場載運厚重石材。<br />\nVolvo 卡車於 11 月下旬宣佈，與挪威採石場 Br&oslash;nn&oslash;y Kalk AS 達成協議，提供自駕卡車服務，能夠自主抵達 5 公里外的港口，卸下石灰岩，過程不必人力輔助。該服務已順利通過測試，且仍在持續運行，預計 2019 年底前全面上路。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.limitlessiq.com/media/wysiwyg/Chen/201811/1330-1.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.limitlessiq.com%2Fmedia%2Fwysiwyg%2FChen%2F201811%2F1330-1.JPG&h=ff181f39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n該採石場總經理 Raymond Langfjord 表示，礦業競爭相當激烈，他們期望能憑借科技與數位解決方案，強化長期的效率與生產力，而與 Volvo 合作導入的自駕卡車技術，便是其中一步。<br />\n<br />\nVolvo 販售的是「服務」而非車輛，自駕卡車的所有權仍在該公司身上。Volvo 提到，這項服務是以重量計價，按自駕卡車運輸的總噸數支付費用。另外，除了運輸石材，自駕卡車也能用於載運甘蔗、清理垃圾等任務上，商業可能性相當廣泛。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.limitlessiq.com/news/post/view/id/7769/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.limitlessiq.com%2Fnews%2Fpost%2Fview%2Fid%2F7769%2F&d=25Bn80kblrlf5eFaRga00ozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=16674283\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.limitlessiq.com/news/post/view/id/7769/</a>"},{"pid":"026cfe44bf078350389b4ed611d4e5dab459db5f","tid":920891,"uid":212399,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T07:20:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea8fab9f963f19ca27f17ea11050480a239fa9a5","tid":920891,"uid":156363,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T07:29:31.000Z","msg":"呢D無人區先敢玩"},{"pid":"c7d4a31a39d619290761a69b065c3dcf5dfdbf0c","tid":920891,"uid":76747,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T07:31:10.000Z","msg":"無人車整個車頭有咩用"},{"pid":"6a13f39a490f6745b3ff62b12605a3ea5506c581","tid":920891,"uid":16256,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c7d4a31a39d619290761a69b065c3dcf5dfdbf0c","tid":920891,"uid":76747,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T07:31:10.000Z","msg":"無人車整個車頭有咩用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T07:32:17.000Z","msg":"壞車都要有司機"},{"pid":"8e62cd6c42c8edd15c61083750c52e23014cec80","tid":920891,"uid":120678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T07:34:17.000Z","msg":"外國貨車司機人工好高<br />\n所以外國企業好大誘因研發無人駕駛貨車"},{"pid":"118a4fa5520841cd3fc74f2e2744be56ee1c360e","tid":920891,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T07:39:12.000Z","msg":"提供服務唔賣車先賺得多"},{"pid":"34b0aa43d3d1e6c45bfd956c10fc5392fedfb2a2","tid":920891,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea8fab9f963f19ca27f17ea11050480a239fa9a5","tid":920891,"uid":156363,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T07:29:31.000Z","msg":"呢D無人區先敢玩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T07:42:30.000Z","msg":"仲要加埋路闊"},{"pid":"7ccd5167cd4d2a235e24b63259fe882ede1d31d5","tid":920891,"uid":133528,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c7d4a31a39d619290761a69b065c3dcf5dfdbf0c","tid":920891,"uid":76747,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T07:31:10.000Z","msg":"無人車整個車頭有咩用"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T07:43:37.000Z","msg":